OL,3,CFirst Minister 'appalled' by actions
OL,4,Cof jailed ex-Reform politician
OL,6,FWelsh politicians have expressed their
OL,7,Fshared anger after a former senior
OL,8,FReform UK figure admitted to taking
OL,9,Fpro-Russian bribes.
OL,11,FNathan Gill, 52, of Anglesey, North
OL,12,FWales, was jailed for 10 and a half
OL,13,Fyears last week after pleading guilty
OL,14,Fto eight counts of bribery at the Old
OL,15,FBailey.
OL,17,FGill was a member of the Welsh
OL,18,FParliament between 2016 and 2017, and
OL,19,Fleader of Reform UK in Wales for a
OL,20,Fshort period in 2021.
