OL,3,CFirst Minister 'appalled' by actions
OL,4,Cof jailed ex-Reform politician
OL,6,FSpeaking at First Minister's Questions
OL,7,Fon Tuesday, Darren Millar, leader of
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Conservatives, said: "I'm
OL,9,Fsure that you will share my disgust
OL,10,Fwith the former leader of Reform in
OL,11,FWales, Nathan Gill, a former member of
OL,12,Fthis parliament, who was sentenced
OL,13,Flast week to 10 and a half years in
OL,14,Fprison for accepting bribes to make
OL,15,Fpro-Russian speeches in the European
OL,16,FParliament.
OL,18,F"It's very clear that Reform is a risk
OL,19,Fto our national security.
