OL,3,CFirst Minister 'appalled' by actions
OL,4,Cof jailed ex-Reform politician
OL,6,FGill pleaded guilty to eight counts of
OL,7,Fbribery on dates between December 6
OL,8,F2018 and July 18 2019.
OL,10,FAt the time of the offences, Gill was
OL,11,Fa member of the European Parliament,
OL,12,Fhaving been originally elected for the
OL,13,FUK Independence Party (Ukip).
OL,15,FGill led Reform UK's 2021 Welsh
OL,16,FParliament election campaign but is no
OL,17,Flonger a member of the party.
